data.description: Welcome to Mallory Park, one of the most highly sought after villages in Lakewood Ranch! Mallory Park is a beautiful and mature, newer Lakewood Ranch Village, that has finally completed all new home construction, making it the perfect time to move in and enjoy everything that this home and community has to offer. This popular Summer-Wood Model sits on a nice, water view lot in the heart of the neighborhood and is close to all the amenities.  It boasts just under 2800 square feet and is perfect for entertaining with an open concept living room, kitchen and dining room that has access to the extended lanai and large yard through popular zero corner pocket slider doors. Upon entering the home, you will notice the wide hallways and beautiful view directly out to the gorgeous outdoor space with water view. The main level features a beautiful kitchen with a large island, dining area, living room, guest bedroom, office/flex room, laundry room, full bathroom, pantry and of course the large master suite. Head upstairs and you will find a massive loft area along with 2 guest bedrooms and another full bath. The owners picked all the right structural options to deck out this home including pocket slider doors, extended lanai, loft option, extra bed upstairs and a full bathroom with another bedroom on the lower level, which is perfect for the in-laws. Beautiful tile floors, stone countertops, custom backsplash, tray ceilings, high baseboards and flat walls are some of the high-end finishes that were chosen throughout this home. Mallory Park is golf cart friendly and has an amazing amenity center where neighbors gather to swim, sunbathe, exercise, play pickle ball, basketball, BBQ or just relax by the fire pit. Next-door is Bob Gardner Park that consists of playgrounds, a zip line, a dog park, walking trails, ball fields and even disc golf. Mallory Park also has a private walking path to the A+ rated Lakewood Ranch schools to make for an easy commute.  Schedule your private showing today while this home is still available!
